  "about": {
    "title": "About S Fashion",
    "intro": "Elegance, made for you.",
    "sections": [
      {
        "heading": "Our story",
        "body": [
          "S Fashion began in the UAE with a simple idea: timeless, elegant pieces that feel made for the women who wear them. We curate every collection with intention — fewer, better things you'll reach for again and again."
        ]
      },
      {
        "heading": "What we stand for",
        "body": [
          "Carefully chosen fabrics, considered fits, and details built to last beyond a single season. We'd rather earn your trust with quality than chase fleeting trends."
        ]
      },
      {
        "heading": "Made for the UAE",
        "body": [
          "From Dubai to Fujairah, we design and deliver with our community in mind: quick local delivery, the comfort of cash on delivery, and a real person on WhatsApp whenever you need us."
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
